"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"# FillType\\n\\n\\nAn enum representing the origin or nature of a fill. Possible string values are:\\n\\n- `LIMIT` – Result of a regular limit order.\\n- `LIQUIDATED` – Result of liquidating another trader's position.\\n- `LIQUIDATION` – Result of one's own position being liquidated.\\n- `DELEVERAGED` – Caused by automatic deleveraging in risk management.\\n- `OFFSETTING` – Result of offsetting positions, often for risk reduction.\\n\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/types/fill_type#filltype\",\"html\":\"</header>\\n<p>An enum representing the origin or nature of a fill. Possible string values are:</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><code>LIMIT</code> – Result of a regular limit order.</li>\\n<li><code>LIQUIDATED</code> – Result of liquidating another trader&#x27;s position.</li>\\n<li><code>LIQUIDATION</code> – Result of one&#x27;s own position being liquidated.</li>\\n<li><code>DELEVERAGED</code> – Caused by automatic deleveraging in risk management.</li>\\n<li><code>OFFSETTING</code> – Result of offsetting positions, often for risk reduction.</li>\\n</ul>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/types/fill_type.mdx#filltype\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\nAn enum representing the origin or nature of a fill. Possible string values are:\\n\\nLIMIT – Result of a regular limit order.\\nLIQUIDATED – Result of liquidating another trader&#x27;s position.\\nLIQUIDATION – Result of one&#x27;s own position being liquidated.\\nDELEVERAGED – Caused by automatic deleveraging in risk management.\\nOFFSETTING – Result of offsetting positions, often for risk reduction.\\n\",\"title\":\"FillType\",\"titles\":[]}]}}"
